<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:09:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>警方：三名不属于国防军的以色列人涉嫌于 10 月 7 日谋杀一名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</link><description>此案已经调查数月，但法院的禁言令现已解除。这三人涉嫌从阵亡士兵身上夺取武器，并用它们杀死了一名在袭击期间进入以色列的加沙巴勒斯坦人，消息人士称该人持有武器</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在哈马斯做出回应之前，内塔尼亚胡就试图破坏人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</link><description>以色列总理渴望在任何协议中发挥作用，他的同谋贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇也有同样的态度。 -法西斯立法</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队包围约旦河西岸城市杰宁的建筑；巴勒斯坦卫生部报告五人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉会见哈马斯代表团，讨论加沙局势和停火谈判 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部称，在与以色列国防军特种部队交火后，五名巴勒斯坦人在西岸杰宁丧生 ■ 真主党发射导弹后，以色列国防军在黎巴嫩南部发动空袭200 枚火箭弹和无人机袭击以色列 ■ 以色列北部的炮火袭击造成以色列国防军士兵死亡，据报道两人受伤；火箭坠落引发火灾</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</guid></item><item><title>为了结束以色列和巴勒斯坦的斗争，两个心理现实必须协调一致</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</link><description>是时候将治疗原则应用于看似永无休止的以色列-巴勒斯坦斗争了吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人要友善得多。在意大利，你可能死在街上，没人会在乎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对以色列和意大利夫妇过着童话般的浪漫生活，还有一位日本侨民，她的孩子们教她变得更像以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列人如何从主要的比比支持者变成主要的反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-this-israeli-went-from-major-bibi-supporter-to-leading-antigovernment-protester/00000190-7f42-dff5-a5d2-7f621a770000</link><description>米哈尔·多伊奇 (Michal Deutsch) 保持着因抗议以色列政府而被捕人数的全国纪录</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-this-israeli-went-from-major-bibi-supporter-to-leading-antigovernment-protester/00000190-7f42-dff5-a5d2-7f621a770000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡派摩萨德负责人就以色列与哈马斯停战进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sends-mossad-chief-to-negotiate-israel-hamas-truce-amid/00000190-7f31-d7c8-a9fb-fff92ffe0000</link><description>尽管遭到一些内阁成员的强烈反对，但在摩萨德负责人戴维·巴尼亚的领导下，以色列将在商定的框架内寻求归还剩余人质。美国总统乔·拜登周四在与内塔尼亚胡的电话中对这一消息表示欢迎</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sends-mossad-chief-to-negotiate-israel-hamas-truce-amid/00000190-7f31-d7c8-a9fb-fff92ffe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长指责本-格维尔阻止将加沙人从有争议的拘留中心转移出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-accuses-ben-gvir-of-thwarting-transfer-of-gazans-from-sde-teiman/00000190-7f7c-da69-adf5-7f7f20090000</link><description>巴哈拉夫-米亚拉在给内塔尼亚胡的信中警告说，如果以色列继续将巴勒斯坦人关押在斯德泰曼，将会产生“深远的后果”，人权组织称那里的条件是不人道的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-accuses-ben-gvir-of-thwarting-transfer-of-gazans-from-sde-teiman/00000190-7f7c-da69-adf5-7f7f20090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准在约旦河西岸修建近 5,300 套住房的计划；非政府组织呼吁数十年来最大规模的土地掠夺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-approves-nearly-5-300-west-bank-homes-ngo-calls-out-largest-land-grab-in-decades/00000190-7f66-da1d-a19a-ff7e671e0000</link><description>这些计划包括扩大西岸深处的定居点，并将前哨基地合法化为定居点内的“社区”。以色列财政部长表示，这些措施旨在对抗某些欧盟国家承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-approves-nearly-5-300-west-bank-homes-ngo-calls-out-largest-land-grab-in-decades/00000190-7f66-da1d-a19a-ff7e671e0000</guid></item><item><title>援助官员称，沙特阿拉伯对加沙的援助受到以色列拉法过境点关闭的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/saudi-arabias-gaza-aid-threatened-by-israels-rafah-crossing-closure-aid-official-says/00000190-7f09-da69-adf5-7f4f025d0000</link><description>一名沙特官员表示，“由于封锁，数百辆卡车现在堆积在拉法”，他担心援助会因向有需要的加沙人提供援助而面临“巨大限制”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/saudi-arabias-gaza-aid-threatened-by-israels-rafah-crossing-closure-aid-official-says/00000190-7f09-da69-adf5-7f4f025d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列约旦河西岸定居者在三起事件中袭击了巴勒斯坦人；没有逮捕任何人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-west-bank-settlers-attack-palestinians-in-three-incidents-no-arrests-made/00000190-7f18-da1d-a19a-ff5c777b0000</link><description>“最近，发生了一些显而易见的严重事件。没有人被逮捕，也没有人受到谴责，”一名军方消息人士说。本周西岸至少发生六起定居者暴力事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-west-bank-settlers-attack-palestinians-in-three-incidents-no-arrests-made/00000190-7f18-da1d-a19a-ff5c777b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长预计将对本格维尔的警察局长人选表示担忧，因为他涉嫌不当行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ag-expected-to-raise-concerns-over-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-amid-alleged-misconduct/00000190-7eb3-d08e-a3f8-7fb344c90000</link><description>高级任命咨询委员会就提名阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德为国家警察局长举行了第一次会议，但尚未做出任何决定。 2015年，《国土报》揭露了佩莱德在担任耶路撒冷地区副司令期间的不当交易</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 18:02:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ag-expected-to-raise-concerns-over-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-amid-alleged-misconduct/00000190-7eb3-d08e-a3f8-7fb344c90000</guid></item><item><title>阻止拜登就意味着支持特朗普。它不会解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-04/ty-article/.highlight/blocking-biden-means-stumping-for-trump-it-wont-free-palestine/00000190-7e58-d08e-a3f8-7fd91acb0000</link><description>我们可能已经集体将特朗普时代从我们的记忆中抹去了，但如果他因为拜登在加沙的资历而被允许再次掌权，那么无论在国内还是国外，都会出现更糟糕的版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-04/ty-article/.highlight/blocking-biden-means-stumping-for-trump-it-wont-free-palestine/00000190-7e58-d08e-a3f8-7fd91acb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 272 天：以色列国防军军官在真主党火箭弹袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-272-idf-officer-killed-in-hezbollah-rocket-barrage/00000190-7e9c-d12c-ab9a-7ffe9f260000</link><description>真主党向以色列北部发射了 200 多枚火箭弹和 20 架无人机，作为对高级指挥官被杀的回应 ■ 高级消息人士告诉《国土报》，哈马斯对当前停火提议的最新回应是“迄今为止最好的” ■ 内塔尼亚胡批准谈判小组离开以继续停战会谈 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它袭击了近东救济工程处位于加沙的两所学校，声称这些学校被用作哈马斯总部 ■ 战争进入 272 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-272-idf-officer-killed-in-hezbollah-rocket-barrage/00000190-7e9c-d12c-ab9a-7ffe9f260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方调查耶路撒冷纵火案，引发火灾；两人受伤 居民疏散</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/police-investigate-jerusalem-arson-sparking-fires-two-injured-residents-evacuated/00000190-7e13-df13-a798-fed3a0b00000</link><description>消防人员在耶路撒冷吉洛社区与大火搏斗后，以色列警方调查了可能的纵火案。与此同时，以色列极端炎热干燥的天气条件下野火爆发激增</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/police-investigate-jerusalem-arson-sparking-fires-two-injured-residents-evacuated/00000190-7e13-df13-a798-fed3a0b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长看到加沙协议的机会，但担心内塔尼亚胡会因政治原因破坏协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-see-chance-for-gaza-deal-fear-netanyahu-will-derail-it-for-politics/00000190-7df0-da1d-a19a-fdfcb9ef0000</link><description>在释放人质和政治生存之间，总理打算如何选择是显而易见的 ■ 安全官员担心内塔尼亚胡的立场可能会加剧黎巴嫩局势升级 ■ 如果公众不觉醒，就不会达成协议，战争将继续下去，并且可能会在多个方面加剧</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-see-chance-for-gaza-deal-fear-netanyahu-will-derail-it-for-politics/00000190-7df0-da1d-a19a-fdfcb9ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官被黎巴嫩的炮火袭击身亡；以色列国防军称超过200枚火箭弹和20架无人机瞄准以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-over-200-rockets-20-drones-fired-at-israel-from-lebanon-two-wounded/00000190-7e11-dff5-a5d2-7f717b300000</link><description>真主党表示，这些袭击是对以色列杀害真主党高级指挥官的回应，预计会出现“一系列反应” ■ 以色列北部多个地点在炮火袭击后爆发火灾 ■ 以色列国防军预备役军官被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-over-200-rockets-20-drones-fired-at-israel-from-lebanon-two-wounded/00000190-7e11-dff5-a5d2-7f717b300000</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 的流行趋势展示了流离失所的加沙人的生活。所有以色列人都应该观看</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tiktok-trend-shows-what-life-is-like-for-displaced-gazans-all-israelis-should-watch/00000190-7dc3-da69-adf5-7fcf05c70000</link><description>由于以色列的新闻节目没有展示加沙普通巴勒斯坦人的生活，加沙人自己发布的 TikTok 视频可能正是让以色列人摆脱冷漠和非人化的茧的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tiktok-trend-shows-what-life-is-like-for-displaced-gazans-all-israelis-should-watch/00000190-7dc3-da69-adf5-7fcf05c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列律师协会对称本格维尔为“恐怖分子”的阿拉伯律师进行纪律处分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bar-association-to-discipline-arab-lawyer-who-called-ben-gvir-a-terrorist/00000190-7d9b-d08e-a3f8-7f9b301a0000</link><description>一名右翼活动人士提出了申诉，并引用了阿迈勒·奥拉比的其他声明，奥拉比称以色列境内的巴勒斯坦被拘留者为“人质”，并赞扬了联合国秘书长批评以色列的讲话。他的律师称道德投诉毫无根据</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 13:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bar-association-to-discipline-arab-lawyer-who-called-ben-gvir-a-terrorist/00000190-7d9b-d08e-a3f8-7f9b301a0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日被杀的以色列裔美国人的父亲呼吁以色列和哈马斯接受人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/father-of-israeli-american-killed-on-oct-7-calls-israel-and-hamas-to-accept-hostage-deal/00000190-7d7f-dbb2-a3f0-fd7f97df0000</link><description>陈鲁比写道，“内塔尼亚胡似乎正在退出（拜登的）停火协议”，并补充说，内塔尼亚胡“应该把精力放在带我儿子回家上，而不是准备一场政治之旅，以赢得华盛顿的民心”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/father-of-israeli-american-killed-on-oct-7-calls-israel-and-hamas-to-accept-hostage-deal/00000190-7d7f-dbb2-a3f0-fd7f97df0000</guid></item></channel></rss>